title: Updated 3-Bedroom House In Diamond Lake
posting_body: ['Beautiful home in the heart of South Minneapolis.', 'This home is only a few short blocks from Lake Nokomis.', 'The main level boasts large living spaces, tons of natural light, and an updated kitchen.', "You'll enjoy the large basement entertainment space and newly remodeled bathroom.", 'Add space and equity by finishing the upper level attic.', 'Enjoy your own outdoor entertaining space with a huge paver patio and pergola.', 'The large two car garage was built in 2005.', 'This home will go fast!', '5628 13th Avenue S is a home located in Hennepin, the 55417 ZIP Code, and the Hale Community School, Field Community School, and Watershed High School attendance zones.']
